text: Richard Rabasa (5 July 1931 - 2011) was a French ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1956 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1931 births Category:2011 deaths Category:French male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of France Category:Ski jumpers at the 1956 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
